		<minRefireDays>45</minRefireDays>
		<letterLabel>Meteorite Shower</letterLabel>
		<letterText>A cluster of meteorites has entered the atmosphere and is breaking apart directly over your area! \n\nSeveral rocks will strike the ground in a localized area over the next few hours. They will obliterate anything they hit.\n\nMeteorites like that are likely to leave behind some resources.</letterText>
